content.body:
### Shop 235/65R16 Tire Size What kinds of vehicles roll on 235/65R16 tires? That would be crossovers, minivans and vans like the Mercedes Sprinter, Ford Transit and Honda Odyssey as well as vintage Cadillac DeVille and Mercury Marauder models. For these vehicles, all-season tires make the most sense thanks to their balance of ride quality, low noise, year-round traction even in light snow, and predictable handling. For some great options in premium 235/65R16 all-season tires, check out the Bridgestone Dueler H/T 684 II, [Continental TrueContact Tour](https://simpletire.com/brands/continental-tires/truecontact-tour), Pirelli P4 Four Seasons Plus, and Nexen Aria AH7. Popular makes and models: 2006-2021 Mercedes-Benz Sprinter
2014-2021 Ford Transit
2005-2010 Honda Odyssey
1974-1984 Cadillac DeVille
1963-1970 Mercury Marauder A newer tire type, commercial van tires are designed to hold the higher weight and center of gravity of vehicles like the Ford Transit and Mercdes-Benz Sprinter. Check out the Continental Vancontact A/S, [Toyo Celsius Cargo](https://simpletire.com/brands/toyo-tires/celsius-cargo), Firestone Transforce CV, and GT Radial Maxmiler Pro to give your commercial van extra traction and strength. Maybe you live in a part of the country that sees hard winters with lots of snow that lingers for weeks. If that’s the case, dedicated winter tires are the way to go; we’d recommend winter tires like the [Bridgestone Blizzak WS90](https://simpletire.com/brands/bridgestone-tires/blizzak-ws90), Hankook Winter i Pike (RW11), Falken Winterpeak F-Ice 1, and Sumitomo Ice Edge. Whether you drive a Ford Transit, Honda Odyssey, Mercedes-Benz Sprinter or something else, SimpleTire has a set of 235/65R16 tires that meets your needs at a great price!
